CustomField.description: This field is optional. It is populated by a user or a data integration. If true, the holder of the account will certify that they have previously had a transaction account at a financial institution within the last 12 months.
CustomField.inlineHelpText: If true the holder of the account will certify that they have previously had a transaction account at a financial institution within the last 12 months.
CustomField.label: Previous Financial Account Indicator
